name: Quarashi
shortDescription: Non Custodial Multi Chain Wallet, P2P Communications Video & Chat, VPN, Browser, Staking, Swap, Airdrops
description: Quarashi Network is a complete suite of solutions platform focused on providing the user with full privacy and anonymity. The core elements of the Quarashi Network ecosystem are the Quarashi Privacy/Anonymity Chat, Multi Crypto Wallet & Exchange, IDO/IEO Platform. All of them are powered by the Quarashi Network Utility Token (QUA).
